Require the BAC, with the assistance of the TWG, to verify the list of contractor’s equipment, personnel and other eligibility requirements, validate the availability and operating condition of the equipment and check the performance of the bidder in its on-going or completed projects to ensure that government contracts are awarded to qualified bidders;
